sHL1jVQ","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"Mecanismo","guid":"qcM8D81SIO9SiMfEU7PQ4w","children":[{"id":"248","parent":"247","text":"Ajusta automáticamente la presión de soporte ventilatorio en\\Nrespuesta a las fluctuaciones en el flujo respiratorio.","guid":"pfhQw2mypVqk48dyRISKwg","children":[]}]},{"id":"249","parent":"246","text":"Indicaciones","guid":"1zyHjgUidhc34kzNVTACSQ","children":[{"id":"250","parent":"249","text":"Mixta < Apnea central del sueño","guid":"tB-hwW4J8ryBJ2zXFf8x-g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"251","parent":"245","text":"BPAP (Presión positiva\\Nen dos niveles)","guid":"hRkG61b4PJ7C8743aHGI6g","children":[{"id":"252","parent":"251","text":"Mecanismo","guid":"I-ygWsvM2uv63r6oNCC7qw","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"Diferentes niveles de presión para la inspiración y la espiración.","guid":"au1XR_kl_5Zw0z3BrdsjCA","children":[]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"251","text":"Indicaciones","guid":"jXqKTJ0oCt8fee-cizh45g","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"Pacientes con hipercapnia o insuficiencia respiratoria crónica.","guid":"jMcnkDdk9zrIhpyoQoOkvg","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"256","parent":"0","text":"Endotipos AOS","guid":"M3wMWVDKtAIwZrq_d-i-xw","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"AOS (Apnea obstructiva del sueño)","guid":"yk2oClEShW30kJcALGQLvQ","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"• Tratamiento: CPAP, dispositivos de avance mandibular, cirugía.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"259","parent":"256","text":"ACS (Apnea central del sueño)","guid":"PgcrYBeOfknd6SiEvKkL7A","children":[{"id":"260","parent":"259","text":"• Alta ganancia de bucle: respuestas exageradas a fluctuaciones en CO2.","guid":"MGnB5o_GQPgtEgl8stqVxQ","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"259","text":"Etiología y factores\\Ncontribuyentes","guid":"oIRRdytqW3w1j1iNb12dWQ","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"• Insuficiencia cardíaca (HF):","guid":"_zz84l_sWVMounfYmJRgpw","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"• Mecanismo: Congestión pulmonar y fluctuaciones en el volumen minuto.","guid":"9mqcDv53_jeh9wCocGnTyQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"264","parent":"261","text":"• Uso de opioides:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"• Mecanismo: Depresión respiratoria central.","guid":"YQYJ9mWszynF6XfUAJLz2g","children":[]}]},{"id":"266","parent":"261","text":"• Hipoxia intermitente (IH):","guid":"MDBTo-Roe78YnId_PZ3WZg","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"• Mecanismo: Activación del sistema nervioso simpático (SNS).","guid":"Jz9Nhbmg0BJRatHQsgBR6w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"268","parent":"259","text":"• Tratamiento: reducir la ganancia de bucle (3)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"• Esto conduce a una disminución de la reabsorción de bicarbonato, causando acidosis metabólica leve.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"268","text":"2. Acidosis\\NMetabólica Leve:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"• La acidosis metabólica leve aumenta la ventilación (ventilación estimulada por la acidosis).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"270","text":"• Esto reduce el CO2 arterial y central (PaCO2), disminuyendo la sensibilidad del quimiorreceptor al CO2.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"270","text":"• La reducción de la sensibilidad del quimiorreceptor al CO2 disminuye la ganancia de bucle, estabilizando el control ventilatorio.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"274","parent":"268","text":"3. Efectos\\NRespiratorios:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"275","parent":"274","text":"• La disminución de la ganancia de bucle reduce la susceptibilidad a las fluctuaciones ventilatorias.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"274","text":"• Esto disminuye la inestabilidad respiratoria y la incidencia de apneas y hipopneas.","guid":"H8opSYa_lWRmMz53QW4gQw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"277","parent":"256","text":"Fenotipo complejo","guid":"Kw7KdvHpAZ9qhUGr50QJiQ","children":[{"id":"278","pa